Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======Main=======
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.53,0:01:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子他们跟上来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人可是约好了一起到庆功宴会场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「等好久了吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「刚到」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是这一类的对白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想快点逗他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果没来 两个人...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想揍风早一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来想偷偷看的 结果失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么反应 太伤人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:03:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我太紧张了 什么都...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.86,0:03:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想得到全部的风早同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛如梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的 只牵了手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 没拥抱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就牵上了手而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 真的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想亲眼目睹 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 那里应该再保持一点距离感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:03:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有同学没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我就来个了精彩回放
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 说来昨天还在教室里...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈 我可以扁你么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 刚才那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 风早喜欢贞子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一样的」是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「梦境般」是噩梦还是美梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 他们俩不是一起来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你们在交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...那个...什么呢 什么呢 怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当真确有其事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 贞子是怎样攻陷风早的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我喜欢上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也跟着一起吃惊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真同情风早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...这样可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是急死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说不是「好像」了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把那个风早...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子果然不简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保佑我交到男(女)朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.19,0:05:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这展开好像很奇妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很幸福的样子 不是挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.09,0:05:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜我是不会灵验的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:06:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年D班 恭喜你们获得学校祭第六名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 一点桃花运都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 你不是三浦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿痞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:06:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿痞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么带着别班的女生到这种地方逍遥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是和班里的同学庆祝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是想去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她们先约了我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 阿痞老师在这种地方一个人喝闷酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们班的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜...甜蜜时刻...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「告白」早「实」太君...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么吗 不是皆大欢喜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师...师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早 这边来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥没啥 有几句话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们俩怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们有那么要好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:07:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不要再让贞子哭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候 贞子在后院哭的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有问她了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以为风早有喜欢的人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为听某人说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你干的好事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿帮了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 不是贞子 是爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不介意叫爽子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别计较了 我只是当昵称来叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你向翔太说了昨天的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊...对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿痞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太 过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是只有你这样想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有清楚明确地对黑沼说「请和我交往」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 但是应该...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了 你觉得那是暧暧昧昧地就能理解的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就去跟她说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实问过「明白了吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请嫁给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚 快滚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这是托谁的福才有今天的 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.34,0:10:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我考虑考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好么 不马上追上去解释
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你都干了什么 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这种状况算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 最糟糕的情况是她答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼似乎没听出是开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全信以为真了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是告诉她只是开玩笑的话 肯定会受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 不要说交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个不好 你就被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就好自为之吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会太晚回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果...我嫁人了 爸爸是什么心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了 把刚才的话忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 孩子他爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...结婚的事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你是想说结婚的事情是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 就算是我不会当真的 应该说...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那是荒井老师说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:13:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fad(200,0)\c&H1B1D23&\fs40\pos(913,147)}让我考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fad(200,0)\fs40\c&H1B1D23&\pos(265,133)}让我妄想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里有洞 哪里有洞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 让你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想象一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象一下的话 就能看到你那无比动摇的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我似乎太贪心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「明白了吧」 不应该这样问的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么重要的事情 一定要向黑沼说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则就无法发展了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请跟我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好待你的 直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远...永远
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我也有很重要的话还没向风早同学说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讨厌我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的 什么都可以说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...不能再以纯真的心来看待风早同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会讨厌你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 我们担心也是多余的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 真羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小矢 把超真心话都说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥 我就是觉得他们很般配而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 觉得自己真对不起他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说什么离爽子最远
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对谁这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对谁这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风...风早
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子和风早进展不顺利的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅她吧 大团圆结局了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是 带着你那些别班的女友回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小矢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C班也是二次会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子呢 沉浸在甜蜜时刻里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子挺有一手的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H60757E&\pos(1075,430)}不是做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs36\c&H93B4B7&\an8}看看日记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H707F7B&\bord0\an8}看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz16.801\bord0\c&H666D5F&\pos(545,368)}另外，这篇日记不是梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\an7\fs24\frz20.64\c&H969B8E&\b0\pos(1033,336)}庆功宴的时候\N穿便服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H969B8E&\fs24\frz25.668\b0\pos(1003,628)}给他缝的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H969B8E&\fs34\frz22.894\b0\pos(634,588)}非常合身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不是做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一觉过后 总有种不真实的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡前的自己 还有这些提示标签
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是现实...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸我... 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是真实的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是找我倾诉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了黑魔术？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子对风早用了...？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说告白的时候 风早的眼球变红了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢 喜欢 喜欢 喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 那不就是完全被控制了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不服不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别挤啊 按顺序来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排起队来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:18:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为接受了黑魔术谈心的人全都告白成功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真...真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受人敬畏 崇拜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是神了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆收钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像...像是在欺诈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 要是有这种好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就有好男人向我投怀送抱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 周围就只有秃子 废柴和白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 幸亏没有人恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没必要担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我个护身符吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式神之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早同学该不会相信我有魔力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还担心这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都懒得吐槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说不是那样的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都喜欢着她的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:19:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼球变红了是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到曹操 曹操就到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早...早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早他啊 「是我一直喜欢着她的」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 那可是宛如梦境哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们懂什...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然那么多别班的人跑来求证了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就明明确确地告诉他们 让他们无话可说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说 爽子是你什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临场感十足
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这突如其来的现实感十足的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得偿所愿我已经不分东西南北了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我静静
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总结起来就是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
