Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HD4E0D8&\pos(373,52)}如梦如幻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs20\c&HD4E0D8&\pos(653,63)}一直喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs20\c&HD4E0D8&\pos(654,242)}想得到全部
