Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs20\c&HD4E0D8&\pos(661,497)}喜欢着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HD4E0D8&\pos(824,497)}她
